{
  "id": "RAW_008ccc0e",
  "title": "内测输给 Gemini，还套壳？！Meta 千亿自研大模型遭延期",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651021485&idx=1&sn=7b2f195938681e0ec56c823a74234746",
  "date": "2026-03-14 06:31:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2b383d3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F5L8bhP5dIqEhwYnfdKwNQnibzG8pGLjgyic4I0gBOfncNCiakfnCR0SEZelQgmuu35jdxjof7eYxvgKpROfXybfR1jwtlERibZPE7lzHTTw4zF4%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p>上千亿刀打水漂？</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503523662\" data-ratio=\"0.04259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97ed75af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicoCrHPEpT0tQiceNphESCa2eJTqstP8G0yqMTkeMFrOGue6kOyCKdTkA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">机器之心编辑部</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Meta 的 AI 计划，突然踩了刹车。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"150\" data-backw=\"150\" data-height=\"150\" data-imgfileid=\"503537787\" data-ratio=\"1\" style=\"width: 199px;height: 199px;\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"150\" data-width=\"150\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0e304983&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F5L8bhP5dIqHeEEzqS4vZbQazSUyaUPsAqIPF1623IpW1oNU21rbEty3DJ1wbumBVE9yMnXsE5wic9eVI0lTAArOAJV2EoEu8KKLjoaxkQzibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">据《纽约时报》、路透社、彭博社等多家媒体报道，Meta 正在开发的新一代基础大模型 Avocado（牛油果），原本计划在本月发布，但由于性能未达预期，发布时间被推迟到至少 5 月。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">原因也很直接：模型表现还没追上头部玩家。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 Meta 内部测试中，Avocado 在推理、代码生成和写作能力上，仍然落后于竞争对手的最新模型。AI 大模型竞赛的现实，再次摆在桌面上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">据知情人士透露：Avocado 明显优于 Meta 上一代模型，也超过了 2025 年 3 月版本的 Gemini 2.5，但仍然落后于 2025 年 11 月发布的 Gemini 3.0。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">换句话说：Meta 进步很大，但对手进步更快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"保持微笑可爱动态牛油果gif表情包\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7933333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"width: 262px;height: 208px;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"446\" data-imgfileid=\"503537800\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5dd69b21&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F5L8bhP5dIqFibT2H6NtfSPHtMlpFu1l4Qb6NS6GpiaGDBJCLrx9TuUCIPbn8kO0yazHCicn7oOd4CcicXQaLl1bsXiblRibxnLMdN97Bib7ib7rmxJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在基础模型赛道，这种差距往往意味着生态吸引力、开发者资源、人才招募能力都会受到影响。因为基础模型不仅是产品能力，更是 AI 平台的底座。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更有戏剧性的一点是，Meta 内部一度讨论过一个方案：临时授权 Google 的 Gemini 模型，来支持自己的 AI 产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5857142857142857\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"350\" style=\"width:251px;height:147px;\" data-width=\"350\" data-height=\"205\" data-backw=\"350\" data-backh=\"205\" data-imgfileid=\"503537788\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bab5f739&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F5L8bhP5dIqF0oj1WYqDyMDnFqic9pmzvxjTUIicRa7QllkJcgZvibZzlwxADNiaFdoSrhs6TcB5Io4dFg83EIORqMazydo8jnGfK3GpnibbYB0f8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">虽然目前还没有做出决定，但这个讨论本身已经说明了问题：Meta 的 AI 战略正处在一个 非常关键的窗口期。如果核心模型落后，AI助手、代码工具、视频生成等产品能力都会受到牵制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">事实上，Meta 在 AI 上的投入，已经堪称互联网公司里最激进之一。几个数字可以感受一下：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2025 年 AI 相关支出：720 亿美元</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2026 年预计支出：最高 1350 亿美元</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">数据中心长期规划投入：6000 亿美元级别</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">除此之外，Meta 还做了一件极具象征意义的事：砸 143 亿美元投资 Scale AI ，并让创始人 Alexandr Wang 直接成为 Meta 首席 AI 官。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5444444444444444\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"360\" style=\"width:256px;height:139px;\" data-width=\"360\" data-height=\"196\" data-backw=\"360\" data-backh=\"196\" data-imgfileid=\"503537790\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0462e1f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F5L8bhP5dIqHJTztpG1UI0mblZrmsYVQ7s3cBj1WWsKCXZBgVx2RGTPrAucDnzqCLBdeeR81a7NntdQ7opncRwSdR3zfpzBViahHWQibYOrLibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目标只有一个，建立通向超级智能的 AI 体系。扎克伯格甚至公开表示：AI 将开启人类新时代。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">而这个还没熟的 Avocado 正是来自 Meta 内部的新 AI 实验室：TBD Lab（To Be Determined Lab）。实验室目前只有约 100 人，但配置极高，几乎是精英特种部队。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">TBD Lab&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">正在同时开发两类模型：基础大模型Avocado；图像/视频生成模型Mango。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"165\" style=\"width:206px;height:275px;\" data-width=\"165\" data-height=\"220\" data-backw=\"165\" data-backh=\"220\" data-imgfileid=\"503537789\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=abe53948&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F5L8bhP5dIqEic0Qs7ib7wRfHCYRCxCqNNJMhmtItRb1Y6hbibLRpK0T4FWMygtWZ9e5LwJDEdEARicw94cFwicicKhcFvrz2lBFMPic485StJfmsHM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">据《纽约时报》报道，TBD Lab 于去年年底完成了 Avocado 开发的第一阶段，即预训练。今年 1 月，他们开始了后训练，团队也正是在这个阶段将目标发布日期定在了 3 月中旬（结果跑票）。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前已经推出过一个产品 Vibes，一个类似 OpenAI Sora 的视频生成应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不过，内部团队也并非完全顺利。报道称，有研究员在 Avocado 发布前离职， Alexandr Wang 与 Meta 产品负责人之间存在分歧，争论焦点是 AI 如何提升广告业务。这其实也是 Meta AI 战略的一条主线：AI 必须服务广告。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Meta 一直是开源大模型阵营的旗手。Llama 系列几乎是开源生态的核心力量。但这次的 Avocado，有可能改变策略。内部讨论显示：扎克伯格和 Alexandr Wang 更倾向于闭源。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"360\" style=\"width:233px;height:233px;\" data-width=\"360\" data-height=\"360\" data-backw=\"360\" data-backh=\"360\" data-imgfileid=\"503537791\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=27f8fd3d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2F5L8bhP5dIqEveDs1puAz4JIHrkzL2jWDVgQQTeznY6yPzpxFhYYkyJZvUfdw4b3CJs851b4yaTVyM9kNHwyI8nqhrEzICuUcbdzUiaA63qH4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">原因并不难理解，模型成本极高，竞争更加激烈，商业化压力更大。而对手们（ OpenAI、Anthropic ）几乎全部是 闭源路线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Meta 的这次延期，其实透露了一个行业信号：大模型竞争已经从能不能做出来，变成了谁迭代更快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">现在的头部玩家差距已经不再是有没有，而是推理能力、工程效率、推理成本、迭代速度。谁能持续跑在前面，谁就能成为 AI 平台生态的中心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">有趣的是，Meta 已经开始规划下一代模型。命名依旧保持水果系列：Avocado → Mango → Watermelon，规模会更大。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">扎克伯格在一次投资者电话会上说过一句话，我们的第一批模型可能只是不错，但更重要的是，它们会显示出我们正在快速前进。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">翻译一下就是：现在可能不是最强，但很快会追上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">问题只剩一个：这场 AI 竞赛里，时间是否还够。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/12/technology/meta-avocado-ai-model-delayed.html?unlocked_article_code=1.S1A.vI_6.4j717gwtFem0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/12/technology/meta-avocado-ai-model-delayed.html?unlocked_article_code=1.S1A.vI_6.4j717gwtFem0</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Meta 下一代自研大模型 Avocado 因性能不及 Gemini 3.0 宣布延期发布，暴露了其在万亿级投入下仍面临的竞争压力与战略转型困局。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Meta 下一代自研大模型 Avocado 因性能不及 Gemini 3.0 宣布延期发布，暴露了其在万亿级投入下仍面临的竞争压力与战略转型困局。",
  "summary": "本文报道了 Meta 新一代基础大模型 Avocado（牛油果）的最新动态。该模型原定于 2026 年 3 月发布，但因在推理、代码生成及写作能力上落后于 Google 的 Gemini 3.0，发布时间被推迟至 5 月。文章深入分析了 Meta 在 AI 领域的激进投入（2026 年预计支出达 1350 亿美元）以及战略调整，包括成立由 Alexandr Wang 领导的 TBD Lab、考虑从开源转向闭源以应对高昂成本，以及内部关于 AI 如何服务广告业务的分歧。Meta 的困境反映了大模型竞赛已进入比拼迭代速度与工程效率的白热化阶段。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Meta 下一代模型 Avocado 因性能未达预期且落后于竞争对手而被迫延期发布。",
      "explanation": "内测显示 Avocado 虽然超越了旧版 Gemini，但仍不及 Gemini 3.0，这反映出基础模型赛道中“进步快”已不足够，必须保持绝对领先才能维持生态吸引力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Meta 正在经历从开源旗手向闭源商业化路径探索的潜在战略转型。",
      "explanation": "由于模型研发与算力成本极高，扎克伯格及核心团队倾向于将 Avocado 闭源，以应对 OpenAI 等对手的竞争并缓解巨大的商业化压力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "巨额资本投入与精英团队配置显示了 Meta 赢下 AI 竞赛的激进决心。",
      "explanation": "Meta 计划在 2026 年投入高达 1350 亿美元，并重金聘请 Scale AI 创始人担任首席 AI 官，试图通过“特种部队”模式加速模型迭代。"
    },
    {
      "point": "内部关于 AI 发展方向存在分歧，核心矛盾在于技术前瞻性与广告业务变现的平衡。",
      "explanation": "首席 AI 官与产品负责人对 AI 提升广告业务的路径存在争论，这揭示了科技巨头在追求通用人工智能（AGI）与维持现有商业模式之间的内在张力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Meta 进步很大，但对手进步更快。",
    "大模型竞争已经从能不能做出来，变成了谁迭代更快。",
    "我们的第一批模型可能只是不错，但更重要的是，它们会显示出我们正在快速前进。",
    "基础模型不仅是产品能力，更是 AI 平台的底座。"
  ],
